asap.faceengine.faceunit

Class AUFU

  • java.lang.Object
    • asap.faceengine.faceunit.FACSFU
      • asap.faceengine.faceunit.AUFU
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FaceUnit, asap.motionunit.MotionUnit, asap.realizer.planunit.KeyPositionManager

    public class AUFU
extends FACSFU
    A basic facial animation unit consisting of one AU value. The key positions are: start, attackPeak, relax, end. This descripes an apex-like intensity development: Between start and attackPeak, the face configuration is blended in; between relax and end the face configuration is blended out. Parameter cosntraints: side valuefits with AU... (e.g., no null for asymmetric AU, no RIGHT, LEFT for symmetric)
    Author:
    Dennis Reidsma
